text: Han Shuxiang (; born 26 August 1965) is a Chinese former cyclist. He competed in the team time trial event at the 1984 Summer Olympics and 1986 Asian Games. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of China Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Asian Games medalists in cycling Category:Cyclists at the 1986 Asian Games Category:Medalists at the 1986 Asian Games Category:Asian Games gold medalists for China
